original_title: Cyndi Lauper - Live @ N.Y.s Highline Ballroom
overview: With her iconic four-octave voice, Cyndi celebrates the 30th Anniversary of the Grammy-winning smash debut album with Front and Center. Taped from New York City's Highline Ballroom, the performance showed the album from start to finish.
title: Cyndi Lauper - Live @ N.Y.s Highline Ballroom
